name: html-parser-react
description: the parser for html string transform to react dom

scripts.init: cd example && npm i && npm start
scripts.version:s: npm version prepatch -m '[prepatch]' && cd package && npm version prepatch -m '[prepatch]'

scripts.version:b: npm version prepatch -m '[premajor]' && cd package && npm version prepatch -m '[premajor]'
